%h4 Hello, #{@user.full_name}!

%p You were tipped #{btc_human @tip.amount} for your commit on Project #{@tip.project.full_name}. Please, log in and tell us your litecoin address to get it.

%p Your current balance is #{btc_human @user.balance}. If you don't enter a litecoin address your tips will be returned to the project in 30 days.

%p= link_to 'Sign In', login_users_url(token: @user.login_token)

%p Thanks for contributing to Open Source!

%p= link_to "lite4commit.com", "http://lite4commit.com/"

%p
  %small
    = link_to "Don't notify me anymore, I don't need tips.", login_users_url(token: @user.login_token, unsubscribe: true)
